  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of our study is to identify the factors influencing the occurrence of a biliary&#xD;
      leak after performing surgery leading to the creation of a biliary anastomosis to any segment&#xD;
      of the digestive tract.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The objective of our study is to identify the factors influencing the occurrence&#xD;
      postoperative of biliary leaks, Sex, Age, BMI, Bilirubin level, Protein level, and surgical&#xD;
      technique (And other factors)are analyzed to study their influence on occurrence of&#xD;
      postoperative biliary leak.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
